  "notes": "Live Shopify capture for public orderCreate -> orderUpdate -> downstream order/order connection/ordersCount behavior. The capture script polls the post-update order email search because Shopify search indexing can lag immediately after orderUpdate. Shopify updates Order.email but preserves the nested Customer.email from the original order customer. The proxy replay uses the same public GraphQL request surface in snapshot-style local staging without runtime Shopify writes; runtime tests cover raw mutation-log retention and synthetic identity/line-item preservation."
